      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鬼门龙王",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "侯通海道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 778
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_tong_hai",
      "speaker_name": "侯通海",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "彭连虎又惊讶，又好笑，轻声道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 778
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一摸他的屁股，似乎仍是两块，但也不便细摸深究，眼见情状有异，不肯贸然入内冒险，问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "侯通海痛得没好气，怒道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "易筋锻骨章",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 808,
      "line_end": 808
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 814,
      "line_end": 814
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 814,
      "line_end": 814
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 816,
      "line_end": 816
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这时欧阳锋已进了水帘，蹲在地下，又是",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 834,
      "line_end": 834
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "飞龙在天",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 836,
      "line_end": 836
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 844,
      "line_end": 844
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_zhi_shang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灵智上人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷莫慌，小僧再进去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 864,
      "line_end": 864
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欧阳锋喝道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 870,
      "line_end": 870
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "灵智上人心想：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 870,
      "line_end": 870
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "巴呢米哄⋯⋯",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 876,
      "line_end": 876
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "遣将不如激将",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 888,
      "line_end": 888
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蹲下身来，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 890,
      "line_end": 890
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 908,
      "line_end": 908
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "震惊百里",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 910,
      "line_end": 910
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九阴白骨爪",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 928,
      "line_end": 928
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大是懊丧，但想这小子已无法救活，不必再理，只好去抢武穆遗书，向杨康怒瞪一眼，心道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 940,
      "line_end": 940
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_yan_hong_lie",
      "speaker_name": "完颜洪烈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那书就在这盒子里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 952,
      "line_end": 952
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_yan_hong_lie",
      "speaker_name": "完颜洪烈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大功告成，大伙儿退！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 956,
      "line_end": 956
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想起自己的匕首还留在他身上，俯身正要去拔，水帘外一个人影窜了进来，叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 960,
      "line_end": 960
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "负着郭靖，咬牙拔足飞奔，几名武功较高的护卫追得近了，她发出一把钢针，后面",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 986,
      "line_end": 986
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叛逆",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 994,
      "line_end": 994
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刺客",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 994,
      "line_end": 994
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉听他说话，心中大喜，听他念念不忘于这件事，心想这时不可再增他的烦忧，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 1028,
      "line_end": 1028
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你干么哭了？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 1030,
      "line_end": 1030
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "傻姑忽然插口：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 1032,
      "line_end": 1032
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "傻姑心中却还是记着她哭了没有，说道：",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 1042,
      "line_end": 1042
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉微笑道：",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 1044,
      "line_end": 1044
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉叹道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 1054,
      "line_end": 1054
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 1064,
      "line_end": 1064
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他说到这里，闭目喘了几口气，才接着道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 1066,
      "line_end": 1066
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沉吟多时，转眼见到那个碗橱，心念一动：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 1078,
      "line_end": 1078
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉听了",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 1090,
      "line_end": 1090
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三字，心中一凛，暗道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 1090,
      "line_end": 1090
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_gu",
      "speaker_name": "傻姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉喜道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 1098,
      "line_end": 1098
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_gu",
      "speaker_name": "傻姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "傻姑连声道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 1100,
      "line_end": 1100
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉心念忽动：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 1106,
      "line_end": 1106
    }
  ],
